notesStmt.note: This is a workshop meeting of tutors accompanying their students to a student conference. It is quite a lively discussion, chaired by S1, who is the president of the [org2] network. The main aim of the discussion is to give feedback on the present student conference, also in order to help S2 and her colleagues with the preparation of the next conference. The speakers are of different ages and professional backgrounds: some are university staff, while others are still students. S25, who is, together with S10, the organizer of the present student conference quite often feels that she has to justify herself. The workshop discussion takes place in a university seminar room.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
